Our Services

HVAC-Drafting

Drafting is the art which represent the thoughts, design, and experience in the actual action. Drafting is very essential part of a project and needs very high skill to understood all standards , codes of complaining authorities and produce final product to convert it in to physical reality on site.

Learn More →

HVAC-BIM

Building Information Modelling (BIM) is a process that begins with the creation of an intelligent 3D model. BIM is an essential and efficient way of modelling services which provides wide range of benefits through out the life cycle starting from design to construct final product.

Learn More →

HVAC-Coordination

HVAC Coordination is very important step towards to produce final workshop Drawings. HVAC Contractors face several unique challenges while working on moderate to complex project like Shopping Centre, Multi-story building, Hospitals or renovating an existing facility.

About Us

Orbit Engineering Services Pty Ltd is an Australian owned and operated company based in Sydney. We provide drafting services, specialized in HVAC (Heat Ventilation and Air-conditioning). We have more than 14 Years of experience in HVAC Drafting industry in Australia. We provide engineering design solutions to our client’s business requirements.

Our mission is to reduce waste, improve collaboration, and accelerate innovation through intelligent modeling.

  • Quality Excellence — ISO certified processes
  • Expert Team — Certified professionals
